creator: The Waiting Game (Bristol) Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
"The Waiting Game offer flexible work in the hospitality industry, specialising in stadiums, music events & festivals. Work for a company that puts you first, supporting you through your time with us whilst working at some of the best events in the country.

Sign up in no time and pick the shifts that suit you, whether you’re looking for regular work or the odd top up a shift here and there and get paid quickly! The app also keeps track of what you're earning to help you work towards that goal or just to keep on top of things

Favourite your clients so you can be first to be notified of their new shifts

Financial bonuses available on every shift you work.

Start from scratch or build up your experience with on-app training and access to further face-to-face training."
